channel.title: Oo0ops
channel.description:
I accidently logged in on an Aryan client on my main. I didn't click anything in game and I logged right away. Now I'm assuming this will be fine because I didn't click on anything (so no weird object IDs were picked up)
No biggie if I get banned I really don't care, just wondering really.
Anyone have an idea?
Thx

Perfectly fine - its the scripts that get you, they activate the inventory, for example, without telling the game that you are clicking on it.
